(469, 'Phage', 'Attacks and kills give a small burst of speed', '<stats>+200 Health<br>+15 Attack Damage</stats><br><br><unique>UNIQUE Passive - Rage:</unique> Basic attacks grant 20 Movement Speed for 2 seconds. Kills grant 60 Movement Speed instead. This Movement Speed bonus is halved for ranged champions.', 3044),
